snippet.title: The Sims 4 Get Together: Official Clubs Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Create and join Clubs where you set the rules, giving you new ways to play with your Sims in The Sims 4 Get Together Expansion Pack!
 
Learn More: http://o.ea.com/45796
 
Get together with other Sims for exciting group activities and live it up in The Sims 4 Get Together Expansion Pack, available now!
